{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 70,
  "title": "第七十章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "吾言甚易知，甚易行。天下莫能知，莫能行。"
    },
    {
      "text": "言有宗，事有君。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯無知，是以不我知。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知我者希，則我者貴。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人被褐懷玉。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "可不出戶窺牖而知，故曰甚易知也。無為而成，故曰甚易行也。惑於躁欲，故曰，莫之能知也。迷於榮利，故曰，莫之能行也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "宗，萬物之宗也。君，萬物之主也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以其言有宗、事有君之故，故有知之人不得不知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯深，故知者希也；知我益希，我亦無匹。故曰，知我者希則我者貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "被褐者，同其塵，懷玉者，寶其真也。聖人之所以難知，以其同塵而不殊，懷玉而不渝，故難知而為貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
